          "text": "Make sure you’re computer is charged at 100%…cut the cord unless you’re pulling an all-nighter",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Go to the library or a similar place…#quiet",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Preferably not your bedroom (it’s distracting)",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Bring something to drink in case you get thirsty…grab a coffee if you’re sleepy",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Go to the bathroom beforehand…go twice",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Find somewhere to sit alone…preferably as far away from the teenagers as possible",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Choose a spot with good amount of light…Edgar Poe was the only person who ever wrote anything good in the dark",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Choose a chair that’s flat…I have no clue why someone would put a un-level chair in a place where people go to focus",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Choose a simple and unbiased",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "wallpaper",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        }
      ],
